Customer churn is one of the most critical problems in subscription-based and service-driven businesses.  
This project performs an Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA) on a customer churn dataset to uncover:

- Patterns behind customer attrition
- Behavioral differences between churned vs retained users
- Key drivers influencing churn

